<HEADLINE>
CLINIC SEARCHES FOR EMBRYO DONORS BEFORE DESTRUCTION DATE 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By KARINA BLAND  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
