Down,'' the protesters did just that. They shut down I-70 for
nearly an hour because they said there were too few minorities
working on state highway projects in the St. Louis area. Police
arrested 125 demonstrators and charged them with impeding traffic
and disobeying a police officer, a St. Louis police spokesman said.
