<P>
   CLINTON MEETS WITH CONGRESSIONAL REPUBLICANS ON TAX AND SPENDING
MEASURES
</P>
<P>
   A7442 BC-EXP-CLINTON-GOP-NYT 397 21:06 U A
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON MEETS WITH GOP LEADERS ON TAX ISSUES
</P>
<P>
   A7433 BC-ELIMINATE-FRIVOLOUS-LAWSUITS-HNS 50 21:03 U A
</P>
<P>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)
</P>
<P>
   A7429 BC-INTERNET-PRIVACY-325&AMP;ADD-NYT 685 21:02 U A
</P>
<P>
   FTC RECOMMENDS CONGRESS HOLD OFF ON PRIVACY LEGISLATION
