<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    MONEYTALK: Personal finance books to read ... and avoid
 &HT;    By Hank Ezell
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   Readers often ask what books would help them get smart about
investing in general and the stock market in particular.
</P>
<P>
