   HATE-CRIMES (Redding, Calif.) _ People acquainted with the
Williams brothers were aware of their peculiar predilections, but
are shocked that these two quiet and unfailingly polite young men
are in jail and suspected in a double homicide and the burning of
three Sacramento synagogues. By MICHAEL DOUGAN.
