</P>
<P>
   SUN-DAMAGES (Albany, N.Y.) _ Think of the part of your body with
the smoothest, softest, baby-like skin. If you're an adult, it's
probably not your face, your arms or your belly. Chances are it's
your buttocks, and the reasons are clear: That's where the sun
doesn't shine. By SYLVIA WOOD.
</P>
