   &UR; SPORTS (s) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   TEN-DAVIS-LONGWOOD (Brookline, Mass.) _ That aged crock, the
Davis Cup, is right back where it was launched in 1900, the Cricket
Club. By Bud Collins. (2 takes) PHOTO
</P>
<P>
   SOC-COLUMN (Undated) _ They mystery of the collapse of
Brazilian's star striker, Ronaldo, has taken on a life of its own.
