<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-13 15:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8298 &Cx1f; sci-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SEA-OF-DEATH-NYTSF &LR;      07-13 0839
