<SLUG> BC-NAACP-MEET-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
HOTEL CHAINS IMPROVED THEIR HIRING, NAACP SAYS
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Md., N.Y., Wash., Fla., D.C.)  (Eds., also filed in `a' code)  
